casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2014-0655. Chester/83 L.L.C. v. Lorain Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, Nos. 2010-3322, 201H183, and 2011-4184. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals.

Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal, it is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
